<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1326700-dr-sowell-is-in-the-twilight-years-and-i">Dr Sowell is in the twilight years and I wish him many more years. He has been a breath of fresh air to me and I am so thankful for finding his books. Clear and concise. 

Who among the current economists and authors would be closest to Dr Sowell views, in a sense I&#39;m looking for the person who will take on Dr Sowell&#39;s mantle so I can have a few others to enjoy and learn from? Thanks.....</a>
</div>
