<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Well I would say Milton Friedman but chances are if you know Sowell you know Friedman as Sowell studies under him and they both made appearances toget<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Well I would say Milton Friedman but chances are if you know Sowell you know Friedman as Sowell studies under him and they both made appearances together. Current day I would recommend John Stossel and Reason magazine which he has worked with. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
