<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53052177-cynical-theories"><img alt="Cynical Theories: How Activist Scholarship Made Everything about Race, Gender, and Identity—and Why This Harms Everybody" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1582386609l/53052177._SX98_.jpg" />
